media.altText:
"Wisher." 
Concept art for "PAPERBOY." Artwork done / signed by @orange_boxJG. Done in May 2022.

Soft, lineless, and mostly-blue digital art / illustration of Matthew Boston: a small, red-headed boy with long, messy hair & a blue-striped shirt submerged in water. Vibrant, deep-but-not-dark-colored water. The background appears to be either a wall of stones or bricks. There are bubbles, little yellow coins, and little glowing yellow stars floating in there with him. Or are they sinking? Hard to say.

Matthew seems peaceful. He is holding his hands close to his body like a prayer. His eyes are closed like he's sleeping. His cheeks have a soft pink blush. Behind him is a soft, very thin, faint, chalk-like blue outline of angel wings. 

Around his head is another thin, chalky, blue-and-white halo with childish doodles following it along. Suns, moons, stars, sparkles. Fish. Swirls. Paper planes & boats. Aliens & UFOs. Circles. Speckles.

Take a chance
Shall we dance?
